on in this room, talking about everything from micropay

00:10:30.370 --> 00:10:34.570
ments to extraction to what is the purpose of a platform.

00:10:34.600 --> 00:10:36.860
You know, in this time and space, you know,

00:10:36.890 --> 00:10:39.540
in March of 2026, we're at proto is,

00:10:39.540 --> 00:10:41.120
and what I've been hearing these last couple of days,

00:10:41.160 --> 00:10:43.730
stuff like the leaflet crew, thinking through, like,

